{"tid":680241,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"睇左差唔多十年波，近幾年真係好失望，想睇番幾場正正常常既好波都咁難","createTime":"2018-05-27T05:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T12:10:53.000Z","uid":24615,"like":21,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"59a943c8f0c082fc9198fcc767ffe8a88cd30d08","tid":680241,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:20:42.000Z","msg":"場場大戰唔係有爭議判決就係有茅招，次次個focus都係去左果d無謂野到，話撚左幾年睇VAR,睇playback，都唔明有乜柒咁難搞。<br />\n<br />\nD on9仲話有爭議先係足球既魅力<br />\n呢d野睇一次就話有noise炒熱個氣氛，睇二次都冇乜野，睇三次就覺得無聊/煩ga la. <br />\n宜家成個歐聯三場唔埋兩場就有呢d野。<br />\n<br />\n以前利物浦加西亞入車仔波，ac對巴塞插水，已經夠d人講好耐。但宜家呢d野變左係常態，大家諗下近年歐聯幾撚多呢d野？（無計對任何球隊 因為好多隊都有得過益）<br />\n<br />\n你話歐足協唔係有意縱容/冇心去解決？我真係唔撚信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今年本身都係諗係場好波既，仆你個街開波冇耐拉莫斯出茅招ko左對面個頭牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對上一次覺得可以正正經經睇到場好波決賽已經係多仔對拜果年，冇大誤判，冇茅招傷人，大家對攻，除左冇左古沙之外（但淘汰賽都有唔少爭議）"},{"pid":"0a75fc50c54d172f146440abd1af45a189cfdb37","tid":680241,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8994779f23fda3ace739da2d2a4595840f587f89","tid":680241,"uid":85284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"其實而家睇波，真係唔好咁認真<br />\n唔係就會好傷身／心"},{"pid":"6a52e95e918ce8b6481991c3e03bcece17c10955","tid":680241,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8994779f23fda3ace739da2d2a4595840f587f89","tid":680241,"uid":85284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"其實而家睇波，真係唔好咁認真<br />\n唔係就會好傷身／心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:34:43.000Z","msg":"都冇話好死忠咁支持愛隊，都已經係抱住睇好波既心態去睇。<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母比d垃圾波我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n四強開始睇 一邊洛賓保定傷 又漏判手球 然後龍門派膠 （真係冇野好講，都唔怪得佢）<br />\n<br />\n另一邊第一場都冇乜野 第二場勁撚多誤判 你又有我又有咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到決賽 又整傷沙拿 利果面龍門又派膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年好睇既得巴對羅馬同利對鏝"},{"pid":"34dd5495862de2868e8bf485011d03e4b19ea415","tid":680241,"uid":8175,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"完全唔覺蝗值得拎冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8640209cf674698d166e74499e0c95b05d452249","tid":680241,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:39:12.000Z","msg":"今場波有D乜爭議判決?"},{"pid":"30742ec10c16cecde302a60c85dd2b6ca1f3c0aa","tid":680241,"uid":27485,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"睇var 拉莫斯都未必有事<br />\n但利個兩下就有可能 紅牌"},{"pid":"3c023e84a45b2be57ccba4d79ed9eeb9ea60744e","tid":680241,"uid":15376,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"34dd5495862de2868e8bf485011d03e4b19ea415","tid":680241,"uid":8175,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"完全唔覺蝗值得拎冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦 猁狗更加唔撚值啦 16強黑撚到入決賽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d8e81873531372d9fb4cc9c6b4c9024155afbb","tid":680241,"uid":24615,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"34dd5495862de2868e8bf485011d03e4b19ea415","tid":680241,"uid":8175,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"完全唔覺蝗值得拎冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"今年其實利皇兩邊攞都冇說服力ga la<br />\n<br />\n利分組賽到淘汰